Interface DynSecCommand

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddClientRoleCommand, AddClientRoleWithPriorityCommand, AddRoleACLCommand, CreateClientCommand, CreateClientWithIdCommand, CreateRoleCommand, DeleteClientCommand, DeleteRoleCommand, DisableClientCommand, EnableClientCommand, GetClientCommand, GetRoleCommand, ListClientsCommand, ListRolesCommand, RemoveClientRoleCommand, RemoveRoleACLCommand
public interface DynSecCommand
A Interface DynSecCommand é implementada nas classes que geram um comando que, por sua vez, é adicionado a classe DynSecPublisher para ser publicado no broker Mosquitto.
